          "measure": "Determine the effects of spironolactone compared to placebo on the composite winratio endpoint",
          "description": "Following a hierarchical strategy of statistical tests including the primary endpoint.\n\nComposite winratio endpoint of: time until a cardiovascular event (hospitalization for heart failure, or non-fatal myocardial infarction, or acute coronary syndrome or non-fatal stroke) at 2 years according to the Finkelstein and Schoenfeld method.",
